371, title IV, § 410(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-08-04"},"text":"Aug. 4, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/794"},"text":"100 Stat. 794","children":[],"tail":". See section 4321 et seq. of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Communications Act of 1934, referred to in subsec. (a)(2)(O), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1934-06-19/ch652"},"text":"act June 19, 1934, ch. 652","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/1064"},"text":"48 Stat. 1064","children":[],"tail":". Subpart A of part IV of title III of the Act (which is classified principally to subpart A (§ 390 et seq.) of part IV of subchapter III of chapter 5 of Title 47, Telecommunications) was amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/567/s201"},"text":"section 201 of Pub. L. 95–567","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-11-02"},"text":"Nov. 2, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/2409"},"text":"92 Stat. 2409","children":[],"tail":", and, as so amended, the provisions relating to telecommunications demonstrations which had appeared in subpart A were restated in a new subpart B (§ 395 et seq.). Subpart B was subsequently redesignated subpart C by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/437/tII/s203/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–437, title II, § 203(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/998"},"text":"104 Stat. 998","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of the 1934 Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t47/s609"},"text":"section 609 of Title 47","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Alcohol and Drug Abuse Education Act, referred to in subsec. (a)(2)(Q), is ","ch